ZH: 他们每个月都会去远村传教。
EN: They go to remote villages to preach every month.

ZH: 她是一名传教士，经常去贫困地区帮助需要的人。
EN: She is a missionary who often goes to impoverished areas to help those in need.

ZH: 我们用心传教，希望能改变更多人的生活。
EN: We preach with sincerity, hoping to change more people's lives.

ZH: 传教的目的是传播爱的信息。
EN: The purpose of preaching is to spread the message of love.

ZH: 他很有说服力，传教时总是能吸引很多人。
EN: He is very persuasive and always able to attract many people when preaching.

ZH: 她是一位年轻的传教士, 刚刚开始传教工作。
EN: She is a young missionary who has just started her preaching work.

ZH: 只有在接受了其他人的爱后，我们才能更好地传教。
EN: Only by accepting the love of others can we preach better.

ZH: 他认真地学习圣经，为了更好地传教。
EN: He studies the Bible diligently in order to preach better.

ZH: 传教需要坚持不懈和耐心。
EN: Preaching requires perseverance and patience.

ZH: 宗教传教是一项伟大的事业，为了改变社会与人心。
EN: Religious preaching is a great cause to change society and people's hearts.

ZH: 传教的路上充满了困难与挑战。
EN: The road of preaching is full of difficulties and challenges.

ZH: 传教的工作需要有爱心和善意。
EN: Preaching work requires love and good intentions.

ZH: 让我们尽心尽力地传教，做一个修正错误的人。
EN: Let us preach wholeheartedly and be a person who corrects mistakes.

ZH: 传教团队每周都会到教堂去传道。
EN: The missionary team goes to the church to preach every week.

ZH: 传教士们鼓励人们热爱生活，热爱信仰。
EN: Missionaries encourage people to love life and faith.

ZH: 在传教过程中，我们也能学到很多。
EN: We can also learn a lot during the preaching process.

ZH: 他已经在这个地区传教了十年，影响了很多人。
EN: He has been preaching in this area for ten years and has influenced many people.

ZH: 传教的路上有时孤单，但我们不会气馁。
EN: The road of preaching is sometimes lonely, but we will not be discouraged.

ZH: 传教不是一日之功，需要长期坚持与努力。
EN: Preaching is not something that can be done in a day, it requires long-term persistence and effort.

ZH: 许多年轻人愿意放弃高薪工作，来传教做一份有意义的事。
EN: Many young people are willing to give up high-paying jobs to preach and do something meaningful.
